version_description: These chords are based off of the slower version of the song: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=_PdgpiAZE9Y.
You don't need capo. This link of the lyric video: https://youtu.be/2DQgjHmGJU4.
Includes chords, fingerings, keyboard and vocal hook.
Corrected chords and chord alignment over lyrics, defined specific chords for each section, corrected lyrics.
Capo on 3rd fret, just one strum on the verse and go crazy with the chorus :).
